execution_plan.description: Retrieve distinct ids of goods whose price is less than the price of at least one good of type 'Tart'.
execution_plan.query: SELECT DISTINCT g1.id FROM goods g1 WHERE g1.price IS NOT NULL AND EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM goods g2 WHERE g2.food = 'Tart' AND g2.price IS NOT NULL AND g1.price < g2.price);
